<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1898,2030]" pageId="1" pageNumber="61">
Body dark brown. Pair of round brown patches at sides of coronal suture and big brown bell-shaped patch on pronotum, scutum with three brownish-black patches, scutellum with a brownish-black ringlike patch (
<figureCitation box="[1291,1361,1934,1958]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 9. 1 – 3" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1977,2000]" captionTargetBox="[239,1341,192,1932]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[214,1373,155,1953]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 9. 1 – 3, dorsal view; 4 – 6, lateral view; 7 – 9, face; 1, 4, 7, Erythria calvusa sp. nov.; 2, 5, 8, E. cuspiprojecta sp. nov.; 3, 6, 9, E. euryprojecta sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281276/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="61">
Fig. 
<number box="[1345,1361,1934,1958]" pageId="1" pageNumber="61" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
). Fore wing sandy beige with veins lighter and with two dark brown spots near middle section of costal or lateral margin, hind wing sandy beige with veins brown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
