<subSubSection lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="64" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,151,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis box="[201,365,152,176]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">Male genitalia</emphasis>
: Pygofer broad with sclerotized appendage at its hind upper angle (
<figureCitation box="[1133,1218,151,175]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 30" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1694,1717]" captionTargetBox="[201,1369,217,1613]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1670]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 30. Erythria euryprojecta sp. nov. 23, forewing; 24, hindwing; 25, pygofer side, lateral view; 26, subgenital plate, paramere, connective and valve, dorsal view; 27, paramere, lateral view; 28, connective, dorsal view; 29, aedeagus, lateral view; 30, aedeagus, hind view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281279/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
Fig. 
<number box="[1186,1218,151,175]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" value="25.0">25</number>
</figureCitation>
). Lateral margin of subgenital plate folded dorsad at midlength with apex rounded (
<figureCitation box="[889,976,188,212]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 30" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1694,1717]" captionTargetBox="[201,1369,217,1613]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1670]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 30. Erythria euryprojecta sp. nov. 23, forewing; 24, hindwing; 25, pygofer side, lateral view; 26, subgenital plate, paramere, connective and valve, dorsal view; 27, paramere, lateral view; 28, connective, dorsal view; 29, aedeagus, lateral view; 30, aedeagus, hind view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281279/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
Fig. 
<number box="[944,976,188,212]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" value="26.0">26</number>
</figureCitation>
). Apical extension of paramere straight, tapered (
<figureCitation box="[248,331,223,247]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 30" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1694,1717]" captionTargetBox="[201,1369,217,1613]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1670]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 30. Erythria euryprojecta sp. nov. 23, forewing; 24, hindwing; 25, pygofer side, lateral view; 26, subgenital plate, paramere, connective and valve, dorsal view; 27, paramere, lateral view; 28, connective, dorsal view; 29, aedeagus, lateral view; 30, aedeagus, hind view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281279/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
Fig. 
<number box="[299,331,223,247]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" value="27.0">27</number>
</figureCitation>
). Penis stem with sculpture on its ventral side subapically, broad apodeme and two apical processes lamellate subapically (
<figureCitation box="[403,541,260,284]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 30" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1694,1717]" captionTargetBox="[201,1369,217,1613]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1670]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 30. Erythria euryprojecta sp. nov. 23, forewing; 24, hindwing; 25, pygofer side, lateral view; 26, subgenital plate, paramere, connective and valve, dorsal view; 27, paramere, lateral view; 28, connective, dorsal view; 29, aedeagus, lateral view; 30, aedeagus, hind view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281279/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="63">
Figs. 
<number box="[467,541,260,284]" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" value="29.3">29, 30</number>
</figureCitation>
). Gonopore apical.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281277/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="63" targetBox="[186,1401,340,1932]" targetPageId="3">
